assmates.com. The Classmates Yearbook Initiative has since grown to over 250,000 yearbooks.{{citation needed|date=February 2015}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{official website|http://www.unitedonline.com }}\n{{Portal|Los Angeles|Companies}}\n\n[[Category:Companies based in Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:2016 mergers and acquisitions]]\n", "name_user": "Moneygraham", "label": "safe", "comment": "Updated infobox to remove NASDAQ listing", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_Online"}
{"title_page": "Nicolas Szersze\u0144", "text_new": "{{short description|French-Polish volleyball player}}\n{{Infobox volleyball biography\n| name            = Nicolas Szersze\u0144\n| image           = \n| image_size      = \n| caption         = \n| full_name       = \n| nickname        = \n| nationality     = {{flagicon|FRA}} [[France|French]]<br> {{flagicon|POL}} [[Poland|Polish]]  \n| birth_date      = {{Birth date and age|1996|12|31|mf=y}}                \n| birth_place     = [[Poissy, France]]\n| hometown        = \n| height          = 1.95 m\n| weight          = 91 kg\n| spike           = 343 cm\n| college         = [[Ohio State University]]\n| position        = Outside hitter\n| currentclub     = {{flagicon|POL}} [[Asseco Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w]]\n| currentnumber   = 9\n| years           = 2015\u20132018<br>2018\u2013<br>2019\u20132020\n| teams           = {{flagicon|USA}} [[Ohio State Buckeyes men's volleyball|Ohio State Buckeyes]]<br> {{flagicon|POL}} [[Asseco Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w]]<br> \u2192 {{flagicon|POL}} [[\u015alepsk Suwa\u0142ki]]\n| nationalyears   = \n| nationalteam    = \n| medaltemplates  = \n}}\n\n'''Nicolas Szersze\u0144''' (born {{birth date|1996|12|31|df=yes}}) is a [[France|French]] [[volleyball]] player of [[Poland|Polish]] descent, a member of Polish club [[Asseco Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.assecoresovia.pl/2018/05/nicolas-szerszen-przyjmujacym-asseco-resovii/ |title=Nicolas Szersze\u0144 przyjmuj\u0105cym Asseco Resovii! |work=www.assecoresovia.pl |language=pl |date=22 May 2018 |accessdate=6 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://ohiostatebuckeyes.com/szerszen-signs-professional-contract-with-elite-polish-club/ |title=Szerszen Signs Professional Contract with Elite Polish Club |work=www.ohiostatebuckeyes.com |date=22 May 2018 |accessdate=6 April 2020}}</ref> His father \u2013 Jacek Szersze\u0144 was also a volleyball player playing in the top professional league in [[Poland]] as a member of [[Asseco Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w|Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w]] and [[Hutnik Krak\u00f3w (volleyball)|Hutnik Krak\u00f3w]], two\u2013time [[PlusLiga|Polish Champion]] (1988, 1989) with the latter club.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uks-hutnik.pl/historia-i-sukcesy/ |title=Historia i sukcesy |work=www.uks-hutnik.pl |language=pl |accessdate=7 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Sporting achievements==\n===College===\n* '''National championships'''\n** '''2016''' [[File:Gold medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2016 NCAA Men's National Collegiate Volleyball Tournament|NCAA National Championship]], with [[Ohio State Buckeyes men's volleyball|Ohio State Buckeyes]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ohiostatebuckeyes.com/national-champions-ohio-state-crowned-kings-of-mens-volleyball/ |title=NATIONAL CHAMPIONS! Ohio State Crowned Kings of Men's Volleyball |work=www.ohiostatebuckeyes.com |date=7 May 2016 |accessdate=6 April 2020}}</ref>\n** '''2017''' [[File:Gold medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2017 NCAA National Collegiate Men's Volleyball Tournament|NCAA National Championship]], with [[Ohio State Buckeyes men's volleyball|Ohio State Buckeyes]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ohiostatebuckeyes.com/no-1-ohio-state-wins-national-championship/ |title=No. 1 Ohio State wins National Championship |work=www.ohiostatebuckeyes.com |date=6 May 2017 |accessdate=6 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://siatka.org/pokaz/ohio-state-mistrzem-usa-szerszen-mvp/ |title=Ohio State mistrzem USA. Szersze\u0144 ponownie MVP |work=www.siatka.org |language=pl |date=7 May 2017 |accessdate=6 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n===Individually===\n* '''2016:''' [[2016 NCAA Men's National Collegiate Volleyball Tournament#All-Tournament Team|NCAA National Championship]] \u2013 All-Tournament Team\n* '''2017:''' [[2017 NCAA National Collegiate Men's Volleyball Tournament#All-Tournament Team|NCAA National Championship]] \u2013 All-Tournament Team (''Most Outstanding Player'')\n* '''2018:''' [[2018 NCAA Men's National Collegiate Volleyball Tournament#All-Tournament Team|NCAA National Championship]] \u2013 All-Tournament Team<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ohiostatebuckeyes.com/historic-run-comes-to-an-end-in-2018-ncaa-semifinals/ |title=Historic Run Comes to an End in 2018 NCAA Semifinals |work=www.ohiostatebuckeyes.com |date=4 May 2018 |accessdate=6 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.plusliga.pl/players/id/30505.html PlusLiga player profile]\n* [https://volleybox.net/nicolas-szerszen-p11496/clubs volleybox.net player profile]\n* [https://ohiostatebuckeyes.com/sports/m-volley/roster/season/2017-18/nicolas-szerszen/ Ohio State Buckeyes roster 2017-18 \u2013 Nicolas Szerszen]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Szersze\u0144, Nicolas}}\n[[Category:1996 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Poissy]]\n[[Category:French men's volleyball players]]\n[[Category:Polish men's volleyball players]]\n[[Category:Ohio State Buckeyes men's volleyball players]]\n[[Category:Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w players]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|French-Polish volleyball player}}\n{{Infobox volleyball biography\n| name            = Nicolas Szersze\u0144\n| image           = \n| image_size      = \n| caption         = \n| full_name       = \n| nickname        = \n| nationality     = {{flagicon|FRA}} [[France|French]]<br> {{flagicon|POL}} [[Poland|Polish]]  \n| birth_date      = {{Birth date and age|1996|12|31|mf=y}}                \n| birth_place     = [[Poissy, France]]\n| hometown        = \n| height          = 1.95 m\n| weight          = 91 kg\n| spike           = 343 cm\n| college         = [[Ohio State University]]\n| position        = Outside hitter\n| currentclub     = {{flagicon|POL}} [[Asseco Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w]]\n| currentnumber   = 9\n| years           = 2015\u20132018<br>2018\u2013<br>2019\u20132020\n| teams           = {{flagicon|USA}} [[Ohio State Buckeyes men's volleyball|Ohio State Buckeyes]]<br> {{flagicon|POL}} [[Asseco Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w]]<br> \u2192 {{flagicon|POL}} [[\u015aleps